				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think Battletoads needs you to support mid-frame loopy_t/loopy_v modifications and may require fairly precise timing of these updates. Battletoads is known to be a picky game about timing. The second level commonly freezes up when the sprite hit zero fails due to some sort of timing error causing the background not to be in exactly the right place at the beginning of the frame. 
<br />
<br />So I'd check your timing and the loopy_t/loopy_v (relates to $2000, $2005, $2006). See Loopy's document on scrolling.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

